{"tid":848550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南極上空測到神秘粒子 或打破物理學規則","createTime":"2018-10-05T04:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T05:55:41.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ef985bb5cd650b69904ffe8291d3588f55ac5efb","tid":848550,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"科學家在南極洲上空偵測到了一種高能粒子，目前對這些粒子的來源和自身特性都拿不出合理的解釋。這可能是將打破常規物理知識的一個發現。<br />\n <br />\n據美國生命科學（Live Science）網報導，在荒無人煙的南極洲，矗立著美國航空航天局（NASA）搭建的用於探測來自外太空粒子的高敏天線。近期，這一天線已經兩次測到來自地面的一種高能粒子。<br />\n <br />\nNASA的南極脈衝瞬態天線（ANITA）用於偵測來自外太空的粒子，比如中微子。這種粒子較難穿過大氣層，因此科學家們把電子設備加載到一個探測氣球，讓它飛到高空中作業。<br />\n <br />\n然而科學家們卻驚訝地發現，它們測到了某種從地面方向而來的高能量粒子。這意味著這些粒子是穿過整個地球而來？但是按照目前物理學對粒子的認知，這樣的粒子連大氣層都穿不過，如何能穿透整個地球呢？<br />\n <br />\n9月底發佈在預印網arXiv上的論文計算顯示，不論這是什麼粒子，按照目前物理學粒子標準模型，它們穿過地球的概率只有350萬分之一。目前為止，科學家卻已經兩度探測到它們的存在。<br />\n <br />\n因此科學家們猜測，也許這是一種人類所未知的新型粒子。新粒子的出現對於物理學來說可是重大事件，並或可能改寫物理界定律。<br />\n <br />\n現在研究者們只能挖掘有限的數據資料進行研究，並期待再次捕獲這些粒子以得到更多資料。"},{"pid":"6e9cfaddb92a9fe9d01cdb83d259899f7dc25e33","tid":848550,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"係地球散發出嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb580a850b88bf431cedf4fbbe9553c903c97c1","tid":848550,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a02755f0a5877ce972b9b330e03f7a5463024b28","tid":848550,"uid":134468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1286b25eb28ba2533594cb2548cb3076d1f1ceae","tid":848550,"uid":190585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">LIVE</span> Science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0f0e9e5eb22d1ee26a7d1309ef07643eaa9b3d","tid":848550,"uid":48276,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:32:10.000Z","msg":"剎那渣exia經過姐<br />\n冇事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cb3d39e1b8ec71b6de944ddc41f5bb9443a048","tid":848550,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:32:13.000Z","msg":"三體？"},{"pid":"d7b1f1222a45f46b5bc16305084fddf9808fb95a","tid":848550,"uid":12956,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"74cb3d39e1b8ec71b6de944ddc41f5bb9443a048","tid":848550,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:32:13.000Z","msg":"三體？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"搵我？"},{"pid":"e0410cedcd68ebbf61eda5dcd6b20ab84130058e","tid":848550,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"AVP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad8f908e5d41220cc458c0108023c5dabb9026b","tid":848550,"uid":58375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"Neutrino本身只會同重力同Weak interaction有反應，應該可以穿過大部分物體，Neutrino由太陽核心走出表面仲快過Photon<br />\n有無篇paper睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n太陽微中子<br />\n太陽的運行情況可以利用標準太陽模型進行解釋。太陽微中子主要來源於其內部發生的核聚變，質子﹣質子鏈反應。太陽放出的微中子數量非常龐大。地球面向太陽的區域每秒鐘在每平方厘米上都會穿過大約650億個來自太陽的微中子。[7]由於微中子幾乎不會被地球吸收，因而在同一時刻也會有幾乎相同數目的微中子穿過地球的另一面。<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0412440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2Fastro-ph%2F0412440&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ea585af7\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0412440</a>"},{"pid":"41c2f30cc06c6f9c349c5b72f264f4711411eda8","tid":848550,"uid":58375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ad8f908e5d41220cc458c0108023c5dabb9026b","tid":848550,"uid":58375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"Neutrino本身只會同重力同Weak interaction有反應，應該可以穿過大部分物體，Neutrino由太陽核心走出表面仲快過Photon<br />\n有無篇paper睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n太陽微中子<br />\n太陽的運行情況可以利用標準太陽模型進行解釋。太陽微中子主要來源於其內部發生的核聚變，質子﹣質子鏈反應。太陽放出的微中子數量非常龐大。地球面向太陽的區域每秒鐘在每平方厘米上都會穿過大約650億個來自太陽的微中子。[7]由於微中子幾乎不會被地球吸收，因而在同一時刻也會有幾乎相同數目的微中子穿過地球的另一面。<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0412440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2Fastro-ph%2F0412440&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ea585af7\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0412440</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1810.00820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F1810.00820&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c33f00d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/1810.00820</a><br />\n應該係呢份<br />\n大家參詳吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726df3fe1de8483eac9ddc6c5c41cb547f405bc5","tid":848550,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"點解live science會譯做生命科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ad87a63fc0d2e0a0e7933bc08b03f6f9543651","tid":848550,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"米洛夫斯基粒子<br />\n<br />\n自護香港公國不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ef60aa6793fcf14dd139a8bc5561db66b55d03","tid":848550,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"地底文明姐"},{"pid":"988d01e2af7ce5a1730147