d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ea585af7\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0412440</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1810.00820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F1810.00820&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c33f00d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/1810.00820</a><br />\n應該係呢份<br />\n大家參詳吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"ANITA 話粒neutrino 有EeV 能量, 所以應該穿唔過地球<br />\n<br />\n不過都有可能佢地度錯."}]}